        <abstract> 
<p>Fears copy of AW’s publication [<hi rend="italic">Über die Berechtigung der Darwin’schen Theorie</hi> (1868)] lost in mail. Asks for another.</p> 
            <p>Glad AW approves of his work</p>
            <p>and objects to Nägeli’s law of perfection.</p>
            <p>Thinks Moritz Wagner overrates necessity for emigration and isolation.</p>
        </abstract>
